name: Deep Dreaming - LUDUM DARE 48
description:
Go deeper in the mystery. May Khan is a private investigator looking for her lost partner. As she explores the town of Truro following her partner’s last lead, someone named Graham Willis, she will meet unexpected people.

All the art in this game was generated using neural networks tools and AI.

A game jam made with a bunch of pals :

Neil Ingle - Katarina Lundquist -  Jana Ribkina - Emei Burell - Mads Skovbakke - Lu Zwanziger

Music by Marten Ingle
